<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.4531698>
    dc:description "Figures 7–12. Species habitus in the genera Acyphoderes and Bromiades. Figures 7–8. Acyphoderes aurulenta (Kirby, 1818). 7) male. 8) female. Figures 9–10. Acyphoderes abdominalis (Olivier, 1795). 9) male. 10) female. Figures 11–12. Bromiades brachyptera (Chevrolat in Guérin-Meneville, 1838). 11) male. 12) female." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/4531698/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

